00:00:00.512 --> 00:00:03.068
<b>Bags often weigh more than we realize.</b>

00:00:03.328 --> 00:00:05.336
<b>Combined with an end-range wrist motion, </b>

00:00:05.632 --> 00:00:09.728
<b>this weight can exert unnecessary force </b>
<b>on the tendons and nerves of your wrist.</b>

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:13.588
<b>A simple but important way to Use Mid-range Wrist Motions</b>

00:00:13.824 --> 00:00:15.872
<b>is to carry the weight on your arm or shoulder.</b>

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:17.600
<b>Here is another example.</b>

00:00:18.176 --> 00:00:19.712
<b>Carrying the weight on your forearm</b>

00:00:19.968 --> 00:00:22.528
<b>makes this repetitive task easier on your body.</b>

